OL,3,CNew driving test booking rules come
OL,4,Cinto force - what has changed?
OL,6,FA ban on driving instructors booking
OL,7,Ftests is one of several new measures
OL,8,Fbeing introduced to reduce long
OL,9,Fwaiting lists.
OL,11,FFrom May 12, only learners can book
OL,12,Fand manage driving tests, with new
OL,13,Frules also changing who can manage
OL,14,Fbookings.
OL,16,FThe changes are a bid to reduce long
OL,17,Fwaiting lists and tackle unfair
OL,18,Fbooking practices.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
