OL,3,CNew driving test booking rules come
OL,4,Cinto force - what has changed?
OL,6,FLatest figures show average waiting
OL,7,Ftimes have increased to more than 22
OL,8,Fweeks, representing a huge rise
OL,9,Fcompared with February 2020, before
OL,10,Fthe pandemic, when learner drivers
OL,11,Ffaced an average waiting time of five
OL,12,Fweeks.
OL,14,FHere, ITV News explains what's
OL,15,Fchanging about booking your driving
OL,16,Ftest - and why.
OL,18,FAre the rules around booking driving
OL,19,Ftests changing?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
