OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1778605560
OL,3,CNew driving test booking rules come
OL,4,Cinto force - what has changed?
OL,6,FYes. Driving tests can now only be
OL,7,Fbooked and managed by learners
OL,8,Fthemselves. Previously, driving
OL,9,Finstructors could also make and manage
OL,10,Fbookings.
OL,12,FIt is hoped this will make it harder
OL,13,Ffor people to profit by using
OL,14,Fautomated programmes - known as bots -
OL,15,Fto quickly book available slots and
OL,16,Fresell them at a higher price.
OL,18,FBack in 2024, ITV News found that
OL,19,Funofficial sellers of driving test
OL,20,Fslots were charging around four times
OL,21,Fthe official rate.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
