OL,3,CNew driving test booking rules come
OL,4,Cinto force - what has changed?
OL,6,FBut instructors must give learners
OL,7,Ftheir driving test reference numbers
OL,8,Fso they can manage the appointments
OL,9,Fthemselves.
OL,11,FWhat are the new rules for changing a
OL,12,Ftest?
OL,14,FThere are now three major changes:
OL,16,FHow many times can you change your
OL,17,Ftest?
OL,19,FYou can make a maximum of two changes
OL,20,Fto a booking
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
