OL,3,CNew driving test booking rules come
OL,4,Cinto force - what has changed?
OL,6,FIf you have already used all your
OL,7,Fchanges under the old system, you will
OL,8,Fbe given two more changes from March
OL,9,F31, 2026.
OL,11,FThe DVSA said learners should only use
OL,12,Fthese changes when "circumstances
OL,13,Fgenuinely change".
OL,15,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,20,FWhat counts as a change?
