OL,3,CNew driving test booking rules come
OL,4,Cinto force - what has changed?
OL,6,FThese are the only rules that count
OL,7,Ftowards the two-change limit:
OL,9,FChanging multiple details at once
OL,10,Fstill only counts as one change.
OL,12,FFor example, moving a test from
OL,13,FNorthampton on June 4 to Kettering on
OL,14,FMay 12 would count as one change.
OL,16,FWhat does not count as a change?
OL,18,FThe following does not count towards
OL,19,Fthe change limit:
