OL,3,CNew driving test booking rules come
OL,4,Cinto force - what has changed?
OL,6,FIf the DVSA changes your test, your
OL,7,Ftwo-change allowance will reset. Any
OL,8,Fextra changes made after that must be
OL,9,Fmade by phone.
OL,11,FWhat happens if you need more than two
OL,12,Fchanges?
OL,14,FIf you use both changes and need to
OL,15,Fchange your booking again, you must
OL,16,Fcancel the test and book a new one.
OL,18,FYou can still get a full refund if you
OL,19,Fcancel at least 10 full working days
OL,20,Fbefore the test.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
