OL,9,Fonwards, learners can only move their
OL,10,Fappointment to:
OL,12,FWith all these changes, how do you now
OL,13,Fbook your driving test?
OL,15,FLearners must book their own test
OL,16,Fthrough GOV.UK. Again, driving
OL,17,Finstructors cannot book on a learner's
OL,18,Fbehalf.
